NNQT_istance: What is the third bodyofwaters in Italy for areaofcatchments?
correct_NNQT_istance: What is the third bodyofwaters in Italy for areaofcatchments?
query:
SELECT ?uri WHERE  { 
	?uri rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BodyOfWater>; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/areaOfCatchment> ?measure; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> dbr:Italy  } ORDER BY DESC(?measure) LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2
